snippet.title: Brock Crocodile SAGE 2019 DEMO released! - check description for link
snippet.description:
The first public demo for Brock Crocodile has been released for the Sonic Amateur Game Expo 2019, head over there and grab yourself a download to the game! https://www.sonicfangameshq.com/forums/showcase/brock-crocodile.349/

To read up on the progress and keep upto date on Brock Crocodile, click the following links below. 

Twitter: https://twitter.com/BrockCrocodile 
Website: http://www.brockcrocodile.com/
